Service Intelligence Agent Performance Dashboard

See a high-level view of your service teamâ€™s performance. Review stats, such as average agent CSAT, average time to close, average speed to answer, average handle time, and more.

Required editions: Lightning Experience, Enterprise, Unlimited

In the Agent Performance tab:

* Details about agents
* Refine view with filters
* High-level statistics:
	+ Average agent time to close
	+ Agent handle time
	+ Case volume and CSAT

Agents KPI Calculation:

* Total cases
* Total cases closed
* Total work items (excluding bots)
* Accepted work items
* Declined work
* Omni utilization
* Max omni utilization
* Avg time to close (Hours)
* Avg handle time
* Agent work volume
* Avg Speed to answer work item by agent (Sec)
* % Work item SLA met by agent
* % First contact resolution
* Agent time to close (Hrs)
* Case escalations
* Avg agent CSAT
title: Service Cloud Agent Performance Dashboard
